0family's%20%26quot%3Bmomager%2C%26quot%3B%20Jenner%20also%20manages%20the%20careers%20of%20her%20famous%20daughters%20%E2%80%94%20%C2%A0Kourtney%20Kardashian%2C%20Kim%20Kardashian%2C%20Khloe%20Kardashian%2C%20Kendall%20Jenner%2C%20and%20Kylie%20Jenner.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJenner%20says%20she%20plans%20to%20continue%20working%20because%20it%20gives%20her%20%26quot%3Ball%20sorts%20of%20different%20qualities%26quot%3B%20in%20her%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20finding%20solutions%20for%20things.%20It's%20your%20organizational%20skills.%20It's%20your%20people%20skills.%20It's%20the%20love%20of%20life%2C%26quot%3B%20Jenner%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt's%2C%20you%20know%2C%20having%20somewhere%20to%20go%2C%20getting%20up%2C%20getting%20dressed%2C%20presenting%20yourself%20to%20the%20world%20a%20certain%20way%2C%20and%20interacting%20with%20the%20people%20that%20you%20love.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESoft%20skills%20aside%2C%20there's%20no%20denying%20that%20the%20money%20she%20makes%20is%20pretty%20good.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJenner%20has%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fkris-jenner-net-worth-kardashians%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eestimated%20net%20worth%20of%20%24230%20million%3C%2Fa%3E.%20In%202022%2C%20she%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.forbes.com%2Fsites%2Flisettevoytko%2F2022%2F10%2F14%2Fhow-kris-jenner-made-the-kardashians-famous-rich-and-insanely-influential%2F%3Fsh%3D14cc60d4368b%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EForbes%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20she%20takes%20a%2010%25%20cut%20from%20everything%20that%20her%20children%20earn%2C%20be%20it%20through%20television%20or%20other%20business%20ventures.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20it's%20not%20always%20easy%20for%20Jenner%20to%20juggle%20her%20duties%20as%20a%20mom%20and%20a%20manager.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20November%202023%2C%20Kendall%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FV-zW9jmYIq8%3Fsi%3DWCslYi_iVuvkrXUq%26t%3D876%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E