ressing%20a%20public%20gathering%20in%20Kurnool%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BOn%20one%20hand%2C%20Chandrababu%20Naidu%20continues%20to%20join%20hands%20with%20the%20BJP%20which%20stands%20on%20removing%20the%204%20per%20cent%20Muslim%20reservation%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20to%20seek%20minority%20votes%2C%20he%20comes%20up%20with%20new%20drama.%20Have%20you%20witnessed%20a%20chameleon-like%20Chandrababu%20Naidu%3F%20Come%20what%20may%2C%204%20per%20cent%20of%20Muslim%20reservations%20will%20remain%20and%20that%20is%20YSR%20Congress%20Party's%20final%20word%20on%20it.%20My%20only%20question%20to%20Chandrababu%20Naidu%20is%20why%20does%20he%20continue%20the%20alliance%20with%20the%20NDA%20even%20after%20the%20NDA%20government%20pledges%20to%20cancel%20the%204%20per%20cent%20reservation%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECommenting%20on%20the%20ongoing%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%20battle%2C%20Mr%20Reddy%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BIn%20the%20next%204%20days%2C%20the%20battle%20of%20Kurukshetra%20is%20set%20to%20take%20place.%20This%20election%20is%20not%20to%20elect%20MLAs%20and%20MPs%2C%20this%20election%20will%20decide%20the%20future%20of%20ongoing%20schemes%20and%20the%20development%20of%20every%20household.%20If%20you%20vote%20for%20Chandrababu%20Naidu%2C%20you%20are%20stopping%20all%20the%20welfare%20that%20this%20government%20has%20brought%20to%20the%20doorstep%20of%20the%20household.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECriticising%20Chandrababu%20Naidu%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BFor%2014%20years%2C%20Chandrababu%20Naidu%20boasts%20about%20being%20the%20CM%20-%20for%20a%203-year%20term.%20Does%20any%20poor%20remember%20the%20welfare%20that%20this%20man%20has%20brought%20to%20the%20State%3F%20We%20have%20brought%20welfare%20without%20discriminating%20against%20religion%2C%20caste%2C%20community%2C%20or%20other%20party%20members.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20RJD%20chief%20Lalu%20Prasad%20Yadav's%20remarks%20on%20Muslim%20reservation%20had%20kicked%20up%20a%20storm%20and%20drew%20flak%20from%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMuslims%20should%20get%20a%20reservation%20(reservation%20toh%20milna%20chahiye%20Musalmano%20ko%2C%20pura'...)%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Yadav%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20RJD%20Chief%20later%20clarified%20that%20he%20was%20in%20favour%20of%20extending%20reservation%20benefits%20to%20Muslims%20but%20emphasized%20that%20it%20should%20be%20%26quot%3Bbased%20on%20social%20backwardness%20and%20not%20based%20on%20religion.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20implemented%20the%20'Mandal%20Commission'.%20Reservation%20samajik%20adhar%20par%20hota%20hai%20dharmik%20aadhar%20par%20nahi%20hota%20hai%20(it%20is%20based%20on%20social%20backwardness%20and%20not%20based%20on%20religion).%20Atal%20Bihari%20Vajpayee%20constituted%20the%20Constitution%20Review%20Commission%2C%26quot%3B%20Lalu%20Yadav%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Assembly%20and%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20in%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20will%20be%20held%20on%20May%2013.%20The%20counting%20of%20votes%20will%20be%20held%20on%20June%204.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%202019%20Assembly%20elections%2C%20the%20YSRCP%20won%20with%20a%20thumping%20majority%20of%20151%20seats%2C%20while%20the%20TDP%20was%20confined%20to%2023%20seats.%20In%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%2C%20the%20YSRCP%20won%2022%20seats%2C%20while%20the%20TDP%20could%20only%20win%20three%20seats.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1715313180000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2F13ba0aco_jagan-mohan-reddy_625x300_10_May_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fjagan-mohan-reddy-says-4-muslim-reservation-will-remain-in-andhra-pradesh-5629932%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Amid%20the%20ongoing%20debate%20between%