quot%3BThe%20Sun-like%20even%20the%20most%20vibrant%20people-is%20not%20a%20constant%20ray%20of%20sunshine.%20It%20constantly%20cycles%20through%20periods%20of%20higher%20and%20lower%20activity.%20High%20activity%20can%20lead%20to%20these%20solar%20flares%2C%20or%20dramatic%20explosions%20of%20energy%20out%20from%20the%20Sun%2C%26quot%3B%20NASA%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20space%20agency%2C%20the%20Sun%20unleashed%20X-class%20solar%20flares%20this%20week.%20The%20GIFs%20show%20the%20dramatic%20flashes%20of%20tangled%20loops%20leaping%20from%20the%20surface%20of%20the%20Sun.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENotably%2C%20solar%20flares%20happen%20when%20powerful%20magnetic%20fields%20in%20and%20around%20the%20Sun%20reconnect.%20They%20are%20created%20when%20magnetic%20energy%20builds%20up%20in%20the%20solar%20atmosphere%20and%20is%20released.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESolar%20flares%20can%20be%20classified%20according%20to%20their%20strength.%20The%20most%20powerful%20ones%20-%20like%20the%20latest%20event%20-%20are%20known%20as%20%26quot%3BX-class%26quot%3B%20flares%2C%20while%20the%20weakest%20are%20categorised%20as%20%26quot%3BA-class%26quot%3B.%20Within%20each%20class%2C%20solar%20flares%20are%20also%20categorised%20using%20an%20even%20more%20detailed%20scale%20of%20strength%20that%20runs%20from%201%20to%209.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAlso%20Read%20%7C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fscience%2Fsmell-of-cooking-food-is-possibly-polluting-the-air-you-breathe-finds-study-5624364%5C%22%3ESmell%20Of%20Cooking%20Food%20Is%20Possibly%20Polluting%20The%20Air%20You%20Breathe%2C%20Finds%20Study%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20number%20of%20solar%20flares%20increases%20every%2011%20years%20or%20so%20around%20what%20is%20called%20a%20solar%20maximum.%20Scientists%20expect%20the%20Sun's%20activity%20to%20ramp%20up%20as%20we%20approach%20solar%20maximum%3B%20there%20have%20been%2013%20X-class%20solar%20fla