%20and%20Dipankar%20Datta%2C%20had%20reserved%20its%20verdict%20on%20interim%20bail%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frs-1-lakh-penalty-for-petition-to-set-up-chief-minister-arvind-kejriwals-office-in-jail-5616157%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMr%20Kejriwal%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20May%207.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Kejriwal%2C%20who%20is%20also%20the%20national%20convenor%20of%20the%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20(AAP)%2C%20is%20currently%20lodged%20in%20Tihar%20jail%20under%20judicial%20custody.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bench%20has%20divided%20the%20hearing%20on%20Mr%20Kejriwal's%20petition%20against%20his%20arrest%20into%20two%20parts.%20While%20his%20main%20petition%20challenges%20his%20arrest%20by%20the%20central%20probe%20agency%20and%20seeks%20it%20to%20be%20declared%20as%20%26quot%3Billegal%26quot%3B%2C%20the%20second%20aspect%20pertains%20to%20the%20grant%20of%20interim%20bail%20keeping%20in%20mind%20the%20ongoing%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Delhi%20High%20Court%20had%20on%20April%209%20upheld%20the%20AAP%20chief's%20arrest%2C%20saying%20there%20was%20no%20illegality%20and%20that%20the%20probe%20agency%20was%20left%20with%20%26quot%3Blittle%20option%26quot%3B%20after%20he%20skipped%20repeated%20summonses%20and%20refused%20to%20join%20the%20investigation%20related%20to%20alleged%20irregularities%20in%20the%20now-scrapped%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdelhi-liquor-policy-case-a-timeline-5284455%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDelhi%20excise%20policy%202021-22%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20a%20Delhi%20court%20extended%20Mr%20Kejriwal's%20judicial%20custody%20in%20the%20money%20laundering%20case%20till%20May%2020.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EED%20Opposes%20Arvind%20Kejriwal's%20Bail%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ED%20on%20Thursday%20filed%20an%20affidavit%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20opposing%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fno-fundamental-right-to-campaign-probe-agency-opposes-bail-for-arvind-kejriwal-5624891%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EArvind%20Kejriwal's%20petition%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20said%20that%20laws%20are%20equal%20for%20all%20and%20that%20campaigning%20for%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%20is%20not%20a%20fundamental%2C%20constitutional%2C%20or%20even%20a%20legal%20right.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20probe%20agency%20said%20that%20no%20political%20leader%20has%20ever%20been%20granted%20bail%20for%20campaigning%20and%20said%20that%20letting%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20out%20of%20jail%20to%20canvas%20for%20AAP%20candidates%20would%20set%20a%20wrong%20precedent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20its%20affidavit%2C%20the%20ED%20pointed%20out%20that%2C%20while%20hearing%20the%20bail%20plea%20of%20former%20Delhi%20deputy%20chief%20minister%20Manish%20Sisodia%20--%20a%20co-accused%20in%20the%20same%20case%20--%20the%20court%20had%20said%20that%20the%20laws%20apply%20equally%20to%20all%20citizens%20and%20institutions%2C%20including%20the%20State.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStating%20that%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20had%20sought%20interim%20bail%20primarily%20for%20campaigning%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%2C%20the%20agency%20submitted%2C%20%26quot%3BIt%20is%20relevant%20to%20note%20that%20the%20right%20to%20campaign%20is%20neither%20a%20fundamental%20right%20nor%20a%20constitutional%20right%20and%20not%20even%20a%20legal%20right.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20agency%20also%20argued%20that%20123%20elections%20have%20taken%20place%20in%20the%20past%20five%20years%20and%20if%20interim%20bail%20is%20granted%20to%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20for%20campaigning%2C%20then%20no%20politician%20can%20be%20kept%20in%20judicial%20custody%20since%20polls%20take%20place%20around%20the%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ED%20repeated%20an%20argument%20it%20had%20made%20during%20the%20last%20hearing%20and%20said%20that%20campaigning%20is%20part%20of%20a%20politician's%20job%20and%2C%20following%20the%20rule%20of%20equality%2C%20small%20farmers%20or%20small%20traders%20can%20also%20seek%20interim%20bail%20to%20carry%20out%20the%20demands%20of%20their%20work.%20It%20also%20stressed%20that%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20is%20not%20even%20contesting%20the%20ongoing%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20agency%20stated%20that%20granting%20bail%20to%20the%20Delhi%20Chief%20Minister%20would%20set%20a%20precedent%20that%20would%20permit%20%26quot%3Ball%20unscrupulous%20politicians%26quot%3B%20to%20commit%20crimes%20and%20then%20evade%20investigation%20citing%20campaigning%20for%20one%20election%20or%20the%20other.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3ESupreme%20Court's%20Last%20Hearing%20On%20Arvind%20Kejriwal's%20Bail%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20last%20hearing%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20had%20said%20it%20was%20not%20going%20by%20whether%20the%20petitioner%20is%20a%20politician%20or%20not.%20The%20focus%2C%20the%20bench%20headed%20by%20Justice%20Sanjiv%20Khanna%20said%2C%20was%20on%20whether%20there%20was%20an%20exceptional%20circumstance%20which%20necessitated%20interim%20bail.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20also%20said%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Farvind-kejriwal-bail-hearing-live-updates-supreme-court-says-arvind-kejriwal-not-habitual-offender-5607580%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EArvind%20Kejriwal%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20the%20elected%20chief%20minister%20of%20Delhi%20and%20is%20not%20a%20habitual%20offender.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20are%20elections...%20these%20are%20extraordinary%20circumstances%20and%20he%20is%20not%20a%20habitual%20offender%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20bench%20had%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bench%20also%20asked%20the%20ED%20why%20it%20took%20them%20two%20years%20to%20act%20against%20the%20chief%20minister%20and%20his%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20issue%20is%20that%20it%20has%20taken%20two%20years%20for%20this.%20It%20is%20not%20good%20for%20any%20investigating%20agency%20to%20say%20that%20it%20takes%20two%20years%20to%20unearth...%20now%20when%20will%20the%20trial%20start%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20asked.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAll%20seven%20seats%20in%20Delhi%20will%20vote%20in%20the%20sixth%20phase%20of%20the%20seven-phased%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20on%20May%2025.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1715308140000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2Fg4i7jkso_arvind-kejriwal-_625x300_10_May_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsupreme-courts-verdict-on-arvind-kejriwals-bail-for-2024-lok-sabha-elections-likely-today-in-delhi-liquor-policy-scam-case-5629449%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Supreme%20Court%20is%20likely%20to%20give%20its%20verdict%20today%20on%20interim%20bail%20to%20Delhi%20Chief%20Minister%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%2C%20who%20was%20arrested%20on%20March%2021%20by%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20(ED)%20in%20a%20money%20laundering%20case%20linked%20to%20the%20alleged%20liquor%20policy%20scam.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsupreme-courts-verdict-on-arvind-kejriwals-bail-for-2024-lok-sabha-elections-likely-today-in-delhi-liquor-policy-scam-case-5629449%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsupreme-courts-verdict-on-arvind-kejriwals-bail-for-2024-lok-sabha-elections-likely-today-in-delhi-liquor-policy-scam-case-5629449%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsupreme-courts-verdict-on-arvind-kejriwals-bail-for-2024-lok-sabha-elections-likely-today-in-delhi-liquor-policy-scam-case-5629449%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Kohli%20Reignites%20Gavaskar%20Strike-Rate%20Debate%2C%20Mocks%20Critics%20Post%2047-Ball%2092%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAnother%20day%2C%20another%20fresh%20strike-rate%20talk%2C%20with%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Virat%20Kohli%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22h