ns%20about%20his%20strike-rate%2C%20especially%20comparing%20it%20with%20modern-age%20T20%20batting.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20which%2C%20Kohli%20recently%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BAll%20the%20people%20who%20talk%20about%20strike%20rates%20and%20me%20not%20playing%20spin%20well%20are%20the%20ones%20talking%20about%20this%20stuff.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20me%2C%20it's%20about%20winning%20the%20games%20for%20the%20team%20and%20there's%20a%20reason%20why%20you've%20done%20it%20for%2015%20years.%20You've%20done%20this%20day%20in%20and%20day%20out%2C%20you've%20won%20games%20for%20your%20teams%2C%20I'm%20not%20quite%20sure%20that%20if%20you%20haven't%20been%20in%20that%20situation%20yourself%2C%20to%20sit%20and%20talk%20about%20the%20game%20from%20the%20box.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1715307960000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2F99ji1fk_kohli-bcci_625x300_10_May_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fipl-2024%2Fimportant-for-me-to-virat-kohli-takes-sly-dig-at-strike-rate-critics-after-47-ball-for-rcb-vs-pbks-5628185%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Virat%20Kohli%20scored%20a%20match-winning%2047-ball%2092%20for%20Royal%20Challengers%20Bengaluru%20against%20Punjab%20Kings%2C%20which%20saw%20him%20reach%20a%20strike-rate%20of%20195.74%20with%20the%20help%20of%20six%20sixes%20and%20seven%20fours.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A102%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Two%20skiers%20killed%20in%20avalanche%20in%20Utah%20mountains%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1715307780000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F24%2F05%2F1920x1080%2Fskynews-utah-avalanche-snow_6548887.jpg%3F20240510035343%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Ftwo-skiers-killed-in-avalanche-in-utah-mountains-13132589%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Two%20skiers%20have%20been%20killed%20during%20an%20avalanche%20in%2