0don't%20think%20how%20he%20walks%20on%20the%20field%20is%20always%20genuinely%20real%20to%20the%20person%20that%20he%20really%20is%2C%20but%20he%20has%20decided%20that%20is%20his%20way%20of%20captaincy.%20Almost%20like%20MS.%20Cool%2C%20calm%2C%20collective%2C%20always%20smiling%2C%20got%20your%20chest%20out.%20But%20when%20you%20play%20with%20a%20lot%20of%20experienced%20players%2C%20guys%20who%20have%20been%20around%20for%20ages%2C%20they%20don't%20buy%20into%20that.%20It%20worked%20at%20GT%2C%20where%20it%20was%20a%20younger%20team.%20Sometimes%2C%20inexperienced%20players%20love%20to%20follow%20that%20kind%20of%20leadership.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDe%20Villiers%20suggested%20that%20with%20stalwarts%20like%20Rohit%20Sharma%2C%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Jasprit%20Bumrah%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F1724-jasprit-bumrah-playerprofile%5C%22%3EJasprit%20Bumrah%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20side%20that%20may%20not%20have%20been%20the%20best%20strategy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20of%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Graeme%20Smith%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F391-graeme-smith-playerprofile%5C%22%3EGraeme%20Smith%3C%2Fa%3E.%20He%20was%20out%20there%20for%20the%20team.%20All%20I%20needed%20to%20do%20as%20a%20youngster%20was%20to%20follow.%20Now%20there's%20a%20Rohit%2C%20there's%20a%20Bumrah.%20They%20go%20like%2C%20'All%20we%20need%20you%20to%20be%20is%20calm.%20Give%20us%20a%20bit%20of%20input%20on%20how%20to%20win%20matches.%20We%20don't%20need%20the%20bravado'.%20I'm%20not%20having%20a%20go%20at%20Hardik.%20I%20love%20watching%20him%20play.%20I%20love%20him%20putting%20out%20his%20chest%20because%20I%20also%20did%20that.%20I%20believed%20that%20as%20a%20batter%2C%20sometimes%20you've%20got%20to%20fake%20it%20to%20make%20it.%20When%20you%20are%20most%20scared%20or%20feeling%20the%20heat%20of%20the%20battle%2C%20I%20can't%20be%20the%20timid%2C%20soft-spoken%20AB%20I%20am.%20The%20only%20way%20to%20counter%20that%20is%20put%20your%20chest%20out%2C%20to%20make%20eye%20contact%20with%20the%20opposition.%20If%20you%20then%20lose%20it%2C%20you%20gotta%20lick%20your%20wounds.%20But%20if%20you%20cross%20the%20hurdle%2C%20it%20adds%20to%20your%20confidence%2C%26quot%3B%20de%20Villiers%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHardik%20has%20understood%20that.%20But%20it%20takes%20a%20special%20senior%20player%20to%20buy%20into%20that.%20You%20know%20what%3F%20You%20fake%20it%2C%20and%20we'll%20follow.%20Don't%20think%20that%20has%20clicked%20this%20season%20for%20MI.%20Remmeber%20I%20am%20just%20guessing.%20That%20doesn't%20mean%20it%20is%20the%20fact.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1715305800000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2F49pjiat8_hardik-rohit-bumrah-bcci_625x300_28_March_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fnot-genuine-ego-driven-hardik-pandyas-captaincy-not-for-rohit-sharma-jasprit-bumrah-ipl-great-5627689%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20report%20recently%20said%20that%20senior%20members%20of%20MI%20questioned%20the%20functioning%20of%20the%20five-time%20champions%20under%20new%20skipper%20Hardik%20Pandya.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Virat%20Kohli%3A%20'I%20am%20trying%20to%20keep%20up%20with%20strike-rate'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1715305555000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-109994120%2Cimgsize-80230.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fsports%2Fcricket%2Fipl%2Ftop-stories%2Fi-have-brought-out-the-slog-sweep-trying-to-keep-up-with-the-strike-rate-virat-kohli-after-rcbs-win-over-punjab-kings%2Farticleshow%2F109994116.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Punjab%20could%20have%20dismissed%20Kohli%20without%20scoring%20and%20then%20on%2010%2C%20but%20missed%20bot