nd%20attractive%2C%20his%20question%20immediately%20made%20me%20both%20self-conscious%20and%20irritated%20at%20what%20I%20knew%20was%20coming%20next.%20It's%20an%20inevitable%20part%20of%20the%20first%20date%20scenario%20I've%20come%20to%20hate%20while%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsingle-mom-dating-men-without-kids-no-fathers-less-complicated-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edating%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20Spain.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUnlike%20in%20bigger%20cities%20like%20Madrid%20or%20Barcelona%2C%20most%20of%20my%20local%20dating%20pool%20only%20speaks%20Spanish%20or%20Catalan%2C%20so%20I'm%20always%20grateful%20when%20I%20find%20someone%20who%20speaks%20English.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Ffacebook-dating%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENavigating%20the%20apps%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20my%20level%20of%20Spanish%20is%20easy%2C%20and%20I%20can%20even%20manage%20whole%20dates.%20But%20it's%20not%20just%20the%20language%20barrier%20that's%20the%20challenge%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNo%20tengo%20nada%20para%20que%20decir%2C%26quot%3B%20I%20replied%2C%20hoping%20to%20get%20his%20judgment%20on%20my%20Spanish%20over%20with%20as%20soon%20as%20possible.%20Plus%2C%20it's%20kind%20of%20true.%20I%20really%20don't%20have%20much%20to%20say%20in%20Spanish%20because%20I'm%20not%20yet%20(ever%3F)%20going%20to%20be%20at%20the%20level%20where%20my%20real%20personality%20comes%20through.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTerrible%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhether%20he%20meant%20my%20accent%20or%20the%20grammar%20error%20I'd%20made%2C%20I%20didn't%20know.%20But%20it%20wasn't%20the%20first%20time%20I've%20been%20mocked%20for%20speaking%20Spanish%20in%20a%20supposedly%20romantic%20context.%20I%20still%20remember%20the%20belittling%20way%20a%20Mexican%20boyfriend%20laughed%20at%20how%20I%20pronounced%20the%20restaurant%20name%20%26quot%3B100%20Montaditos%26quot%3B%20in%202012.%20All%20this%20has%20very%20much%20shaped%20my%20attitude%20toward%20the%20language%20and%20how%20I%20feel%20speaking%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22871345da-d47f-4b1d-ad7a-f7368f16efdc%5C%22%3EI'm%20overly%20compliant%20and%20naive%20in%20Spanish%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20not%20just%20unpleasant%20memories%20that%20are%20to%20blame%20for%20my%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsingle-mom-dating-life-with-teenage-kids-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eunwillingness%20to%20date%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20Spanish.%20There's%20also%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thelocal.se%2F20221102%2Fhej-hello-hola-does-your-personality-change-when-you-speak-another-language-stockholm-university-tlccu%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eresearch%20%3C%2Fa%3Ethat%20suggests%20personalities%20can%20change%20when%20you're%20speaking%20another%20language.%20%26quot%3BEnvironmental%20cues%2C%20such%20as%20language%20use%2C%20can%20lead%20to%20adjustments%20in%20mood%20and%20demeanor.%20Multilinguals%20often%20use%20different%20languages%20for%20distinct%20purposes%2C%20and%20those%20purposes%20will%20influence%20your%20emotional%20states%2C%26quot%3B%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nateyoung.se%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3ENate%20Young%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20a%20former%20Marie%20Sklodowska-Curie%20Fellow%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Oslo%20who%20worked%20on%20the%20study%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20Young%3C%2Fspan%3E%20holds%20a%20Ph.D.%20in%20Linguistics%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0from%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EQueen%20Mary%2C%20University%20of%20London%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20as%20much%20of%20my%20experience%20in%20Spain%20involves%20frustration%20with%20my%20own%20language%20limits%2C%20it's%20shaped%20how%20I%20feel%20when%20speaking%20the%20language.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20result%20of%20this%20is%20what%20some%20refer%20to%20as%20%26quot%3Bnodding%20dog