%3Cp%3EAt%20an%20event%20organised%20here%20by%20the%20Council%20on%20Foreign%20Relations%2C%20a%20top%20American%20think-tank%2C%20US%20Ambassador%20to%20India%20Eric%20Garcetti%20told%20the%20audience%20he%20was%20confident%20that%20%26quot%3B10%20years%20from%20now%20India%20is%20going%20to%20be%20a%20vibrant%20democracy%20as%20it%20is%20today%20in%20terms%20of%20free%20and%20fair%20elections%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAgain%20there's%20things%20that%20probably%20are%20worse%20and%20there's%20things%20that%20are%20better.%20They%20have%20a%20law%2C%20you%20can't%20go%20more%20than%20two%20kilometers%20to%20vote.%20So%20there''ll%20be%20one%20guy%20who%20lives%20in%20the%20mountains%20as%20a%20monk%20(at)%20someplace.%20They%20will%20walk%20for%20two%20days%20to%20bring%20the%20voting%20machine%2C%20execute%20the%20vote%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20responding%20to%20a%20question%20expressing%20concerns%20over%20the%20status%20of%20democracy%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20that%20during%20elections%20times%20in%20India%2C%20there%20are%20people%20who%20check%20trucks%20to%20make%20sure%20that%20nobody%20has%20cash%20going%20around.%20%26quot%3BThere's%20probably%20walk-in%20money%2C%20as%20they%20call%20it%20in%20some%20cities%20here%20in%20the%20United%20States%2C%20Philadelphia%2C%20that's%20like%20a%20tradition%20where%20cash%20kind%20of%20gets%20you%20votes%20and%20things%20like%20that.%20So%2C%20I've%20been%20impressed%20with%20certain%20things%20they%20do%20that%20are%20better%20than%20us.%26quot%3B%20He%2C%20however%2C%20added%20there%20are%20things%20that%20%26quot%3Bwe%20keep%20our%20eyes%20on.%20And%20I%20just%20disagree%20that%20we%20don't%20speak%20out%20about%20them%26quot%3B%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20put%20them%20out.%20It's%20not%20the%20only%20thing.%20I%20mean%2C%20some%20people%20want%20us%20to%20only%20say%20that.%20But%20this%20is%20too%20important%20a%20relationship%20to%20spend%20all%20day%20long%20only%20saying%20that%20over%20and%20over.%20You're%20not%20going%20to%20get%20anything%20else%20done.%20It'll%20become%20a%20self-fulfilling%20prophecy%20that%20they%20will%20not%20be%20close%20to%20us.%20Whereas%20where%20we%20find%20the%20common%20ground%2C%20which%20I%20think%20is%20really%20human%20to%20human%2C%20very%20deep%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20have%20a%20lot%20of%20leaders%20there%20who%20have%20come%20worked%2C%20been%20educated%20here%2C%20have%20an%20affinity.%20There's%20a%20huge%20positive%20polling%20of%20Americans.%20I%20told%20the%20president%20before%20the%20state%20visit%20that%20Americans%20poll%20better%20in%20India%20than%20Americans%20do%20in%20America.%20They%20like%20us%20more%20than%20we%20like%20ourselves.%20That's%20rare%20in%20the%20world%20today%2C%26quot%3B%20Garcetti%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20Poland%20is%20the%20only%20other%20country%20that%20comes%20close.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20a%20huge%20advantage%20for%20the%20US%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B...%20If%20you%20don't%20know%20state%20governments%20in%20India%2C%20which%20are%20as%20powerful%20as%20the%20centre%20and%20are%20run%20by%20opposition%20parties%2C%20and%20there's%20plenty%20of%20criticisms%20you%20can%20make%2C%20too%2C%20about%20other%20parties%20that%20have%20been%20in%20power.%20If%20you%20look%20at%20history%20in%20India%2C%20there's%20not%20been%20some%20golden%20era%20where%20everybody's%20rights%20have%20been%20respected%2C%26quot%3B%20Garcetti%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAmerica's%20role%20is%20to%20stand%20up%20for%20the%20principles%20and%20the%20values%20that%20we%20have%2C%20to%20never%20retreat%20from%20those%20and%20talk%20about%20them.%20But%20is%20the%20relationship%20only%20that%20and%20those%20points%20of%20conflict%3F%20Absolutely%20not.%20It%20would%20be%20bad%20diplomacy%2C%20it%20would%20be%20bad%20policy.%20But%20in%20my%20heart%2C%20100%20percent%2C%20I%20believe%2C%20not%20only%20will%20this%2