ance%20of%20dai%20pai%20dongs%20in%20Hong%20Kong%20is%20most%20likely%20related%20to%20policies%3A%20the%20government%20no%20longer%20issues%20new%20licenses%2C%20and%20those%20who%20own%20the%20remaining%20licenses%20cannot%20continue%20operating%20if%20no%20one%20takes%20over%20the%20business%2C%26quot%3B%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fyanwei525%2F%3Fhl%3Den%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAgnes%20Chee%20Yan-Wei%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20author%20of%20%26quot%3BVanishing%20Flavours%20of%20Cantonese%20Cuisine%2C%26quot%3B%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20number%20of%20dai%20pai%20dongs%20in%20all%20of%20Hong%20Kong%20has%20dwindled%20to%20just%20over%2020%2C%20according%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.discoverhongkong.com%2Fseasia%2Fexplore%2Fdining%2Fmust-try-dai-pai-dongs-and-their-essential-dishes.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EHong%20Kong%20Tourism%20Board%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20government%20ceased%20issuing%20new%20licenses%20in%20the%201970s%2C%20and%20those%20still%20running%20are%20now%20only%20transferrable%20to%20family%20members.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETiffany%20%3Cspan%3ELeung%2C%20a%20food%20critic%3C%2Fspan%3E%20from%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Ftop_hongkong_restaurants%2F%3Fhl%3Den%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EHK's%20Top%20Restaurants%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20described%20dai%20pai%20dogs%20as%20''one-of-a-kind%26quot%3B%20experiences.%20%26quot%3BIt%20is%20upsetting%20to%20note%20that%20dai%20pai%20dongs%20could%20not%20keep%20up%20with%20the%20fast%20development%20pace%20of%20Hong%20Kong%20and%20are%20gradually%20being%20replaced%20by%20modern%20alternatives%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Man%20eating%20at%20a%20table%20at%20Dai%20Lee%20Dai%20Pai%20Dong%2C%20a%20wet%20market%20in%20Hong%20Kong.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6639cf91ec0c696569019ef7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%2