2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ECustomers%20like%20Tony%20Lee%2C%2058%2C%20are%20loyal.%20%26quot%3BWe%20like%20coming%20here%20because%20you%20can%20be%20loud%20and%20obnoxious%2C%20and%20no%20one%20would%20look%20at%20you%20differently%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BOnce%20we%20found%20this%20dai%20pai%20dong%2C%20we%20started%20meeting%20here%20twice%20a%20week.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20customer%2C%20Mok%20Wah%20Ho%2C%2067%2C%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20like%20coming%20to%20dai%20pai%20dongs%20because%20the%20beers%20are%20cold%2C%20the%20food%20portions%20are%20big%2C%20and%20prices%20are%20very%20reasonable.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2214937b6c-7224-40f7-a8af-95ef8eb875d7%5C%22%3EChoi's%20goal%20is%20to%20uphold%20the%20tradition%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EChoi%20is%20proud%20of%20their%20reputation.%20%26quot%3BOur%20stall%20has%20been%20a%20beloved%20fixture%20for%20years%20%E2%80%94%20my%20aspiration%20is%20to%20perpetuate%20this%20cherished%20legacy%20and%20uphold%20the%20tradition%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20challenges%20abound.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChoi%20has%20observed%20a%20staff%20shortage%20at%20many%20dia%20pai%20dongs%2C%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhiring-gen-z-graduates-pay-transparency-adobe-2023-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efewer%20young%20people%20wanting%20to%20apply%20to%20jobs%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20require%20long%20hours.%20Employers%20are%20finding%20it%20hard%20to%20recruit%20amid%20Hong%20Kong's%20shrinking%20population%20and%20the%20city's%20minimum%20wage%20not%20keeping%20up%20with%20inflation%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.scmp.com%2Fcomment%2Fletters%2Farticle%2F3219275%2Ffixing-hong-kongs-worker-shortage-will-not-be-quick-or-easy%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESouth%20China%20Morning%20Post%3C%2Fa%3E%20reported%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Choi's%20staff%2C%20who%20have%20worked%20with%20them%20for%20over%20a%20decade%2C%20are%20aging.%20Most%20of%20them%20are%20between%2050%20and%2060%2C%20with%20a%20few%20members%20of%20the%20team%20already%20in%20their%2070s.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20intricate%20skills%20of%20managing%20our%20staff%2C%20maintaining%20vendor%20relations%2C%20and%20building%20customer%20relationships%20were%20things%20I%20had%20to%20learn%20on%20the%20fly%20during%20the%20early%20years%20of%20management%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BThis%20was%20particularly%20difficult%20because%20I%20was%20younger%20and%20respect%20had%20to%20be%20earned.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221600%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Group%20of%20people%20from%20Young%20Master%20Ales%20and%20Dai%20Lee%20Dai%20Pai%20Dong%20in%20Hong%20Kong%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6639d716ec0c696569019f2b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EToby%20To%20Yan%20Choi%20worked%20with%20Hong%20Kong's%20top%20craft%20brewery%2C%20Young%20Master%20Ales.%3Cp%3EToby%20To%20Yan%20Choi%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2277278fef-3471-4d11-b9af-8912ecfa8178%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EHe's%20hoping%20craft%20beer%20can%20help%20entice%20younger%20diners%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20effort%20to%20infuse%20fresh%20energy%20into%20the%20business%2C%20Choi%20has%20partnered%20with%20local%20beer%20breweries%2C%20such%20as%20Young%20Master%20Ale%2C%20to%20organize%20events%20and%20draw%20in%20a%20younger%20crowd.%20He's%20also%20collaborated%20with%20local%20tour%20companies%20to%20attract%20more%20tourists.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDai%20pai%20dongs%20are%20a%20crucial%20part%20of%20remembering%20and%20preserving%20Hong%20Kong's%20food%20history%20%E2%80%94%20when%20we%20eat%20at%20there%20we%20enjoy%20a%20taste%20of%20the%20past%2C%20and%20help%20ensure%20that%20Cantonese%20culinary%20culture%20continues%20into%20the%20future%2C%26quot%3B%20