-us-bomb-kit-ukraine-leaked-documents-2023-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EJoint%20Direct%20Attack%20Munitions%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20throughout%20the%20war%2C%20but%20widespread%20Russian%20electronic%20warfare%20is%20regularly%20diminishing%20the%20effectiveness%20of%20these%20weapons.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELt.%20Gen.%20Antonio%20Aguto%2C%20who%20is%20serving%20as%20the%20commander%20of%20Security%20Assistance%20Group-Ukraine%2C%20addressed%20the%20problem%20in%20December%202023%2C%20noting%20that%20electronic%20warfare%20directed%20at%20some%20of%20the%20US'%20%26quot%3Bmost%20precise%20capabilities%20is%20a%20challenge.%26quot%3B%20Other%20US%20officials%20have%20identified%20these%20issues%20as%20well%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20US%20and%20Ukraine%20were%20working%20on%20solutions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAny%20fixes%20developed%20to%20effectively%20counter%20the%20challenge%20posed%20by%20electronic%20warfare%20won't%20just%20benefit%20Ukraine.%20They'll%20also%20help%20the%20US%20solve%20problems%20it%20has%20long%20been%20concerned%20about%20as%20it%20prepares%20for%20the%20possibility%20of%20great-power%20conflict.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMark%20Cancian%2C%20a%20retired%20Marine%20Corps%20colonel%20and%20a%20senior%20advisor%20at%20the%20Center%20for%20Strategic%20and%20International%20Studies%2C%20explained%20to%20Business%20Insider%20that%20%26quot%3Bthe%20widespread%20GPS%20spoofing%20we%20see%20in%20Ukraine%20adds%20urgency%20to%20solving%20a%20problem%20DoD%20has%20long%20recognized%3A%20that%20wartime%20spoofing%20will%20reduce%20the%20effectiveness%20of%20its%20weapons.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Vehicles%20with%20tall%20poles%20attached%20to%20them.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64a2e6639fab2b00184af038%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22800%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20Russian%20R-330Zh%20Zhitel%20electronic-warfare%20jamming%20station%20during%20an%20exercise%20in%20July%