ts%20precision%20weapons%20should%20it%20one%20day%20find%20itself%20in%20a%20war%20with%20another%20great%20power%2C%20be%20it%20Russia%20or%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-drones-glitching-getting-lost-in-ukraine-picking-chinese-ones-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EChina%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20would%20almost%20certainly%20employ%20electronic%20warfare%20as%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWithington%20said%20that%20%26quot%3Beven%20if%20that%20jamming%20has%20been%20quite%20successful%2C%20the%20tactical%20imperative%20behind%20this%20is%20to%20work%20out%20a%20way%20to%20outflank%20the%20effectiveness%20of%20that%20electronic%20attack%2C%26quot%3B%20noting%20that%20while%20a%20strong%20Russian%20jamming%20signal%20may%20be%20effective%2C%20it's%20also%20easier%20to%20detect%20and%20destroy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20a%20media%20event%20earlier%20this%20month%2C%20Doug%20Bush%2C%20the%20Army's%20acquisition%20chief%2C%20said%20it%20wasn't%20surprising%20Russia%20was%20able%20to%20jam%20US%20weapons.%20He%20said%20it%20was%20part%20of%20a%20%26quot%3Bconstant%20cycle%26quot%3B%20of%20innovation%20on%20both%20sides%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20US%20was%20learning%20that%20%26quot%3Bwith%20any%20precision%20weapon%2C%20you%20want%20multiple%20ways%20to%20guide%20it%20to%20its%20target.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20some%20weapons%2C%20that's%20already%20in%20the%20works.%20Earlier%20this%20week%2C%20the%20US%20Air%20Force%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.defense.gov%2FNews%2FContracts%2FContract%2FArticle%2F3765102%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eannounced%3C%2Fa%3E%20a%20contract%20for%20add-on%20seekers%20for%20its%20extended-range%20JDAMs%2C%20the%20goal%20being%20to%20improve%20the%20JDAM%20to%20resist%20electronic%20jamming%20and%20instead%20lock%20onto%20the%20source%20of%20the%20jamming%2C%20targeting%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBush%20said%20the%20Army%20had%20created%20a%20team%20focused%20on%20adapting%20its%20weapons%20to%20electronic%20warfare%20issues%20long%20before%20the%20war%20in%20Ukraine%2C%20signaling%20the%20Pentagon's%20clear%20understanding%20of%20the%20problem%20these%20capabilities%20pose.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBush%20previously%20said%20in%20August%202023%20that%20the%20Army%20was%20%26quot%3Bfundamentally%20reinvesting%20in%20rebuilding%20our%20tactical%20electronic-warfare%20capability%20after%20that%20largely%20left%20the%20force%20over%20the%20last%2020%20years%26quot%3B%20and%20that%20the%20war%20in%20Ukraine%20had%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fukraine-russia-war-us-army-urgently-working-on-electronic-warfare-2023-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eadded%20%26quot%3Burgency%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20those%20efforts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Soldiers%20setting%20up%20portable%20packs.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F653fd01e356802a56be7786c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221333%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EUS%20Army%20electronic-warfare%20specialists%20set%20up%20portable%20packs%20capable%20of%20picking%20up%20and%20jamming%20enemy%20frequencies%20at%20Fort%20Bliss%20in%20Texas%20in%20December%202018.%3Cp%3EStaff%20Sgt.%20Felicia%20Jagdatt%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EEfforts%20to%20adapt%20precision%20weapons%20to%20the%20threat%20is%20just%20one%20facet%20of%20a%20multi-layered%20solution%2C%20Withington%20said.%20Other%20solutions%20to%20the%20problem%20involve%20using%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fvideo-us-harpoon-missiles-destroy-a-heavily-armed-russian-vessel-in-black-sea-2022-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eother%20weapons%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20prioritizing%20targeting%20the%20point%20of%20origin%20for%20electronic%20warfare%20signals%20early%20in%20a%20conflict.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20imperative%20that%20forces%20like%20the%20US%20and%20its%20allies%20see%20future%20battle%20in%20a%20case%20that%20they%20have%20to%20first%20establish%20electromagnetic%20superiority%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20explaining%20that%20denying%20enemies%20from%20using%20the%20electromagnetic%20spectrum%20in%20any%20way%20would%20%26quot%3Bmassively%20degrade%20at%20the%20very%20least%2C%20if%20not%20prevent%20altogether%26quot%3B%20an%20enemy%20from%20interfering%20with%20its%20weapons.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUltimately%2C%20though%2C%20as%20the%20US%20and%20Ukraine%20adjust%20to%20Russia's%20jamming%20and%20learn%20from%20the%20war%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdecoy-arms-race-playing-out-ukraine-harder-fake-tanks-weapons-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%26quot%3Bconstant%20cycle%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20innovation%2C%20as%20Bush%20said%2C%20will%20continue.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20measure%2C%20counter-measure%2C%20counter-countermeasure%20that%20we're%20seeing%20in%20Ukraine%20is%20typical%20in%20war%2C%26quot%3B%20Cancian%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20there%20is%20%26quot%3Bno%20technology%20provides%20the%20ultimate%20advantage.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frussian-electronic-warfare-shows-us-needs-for-future-wars-2024-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1715289572000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F663cde57b4abc992e8c7421d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frussian-electronic-warfare-shows-us-needs-for-future-wars-2024-5%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Russia%20keeps%20jamming%20US%20precision%20weapons%20in%20Ukraine%2C%20showing%20the%20US%20a%20problem%20it%20needs%20to%20solve%20before%20its%20next%20big%20fight.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22cpanella%40businessinsider.com%20(Chris%20Panella%2CJake%20Epstein)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A101%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com