re%20performance%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20Samsung%20S95D%20TV%20in%20a%20living%20room%20with%20a%20video%20of%20rippling%20water%20on%20the%20screen.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66143c7a3f923f7dab05a4d9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20S95D%20(pictured%20above)%20edges%20out%20the%20S95C%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20HDR%20brightness%20capabilities.%3Cp%3ESteven%20Cohen%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20S95D%20and%20S95C%20both%20use%20QD-OLED%20(OLED%20with%20quantum%20dots)%20panels%2C%20which%20enables%20them%20to%20produce%20pixel-level%20contrast%20control%20and%20a%20wide%20range%20of%20bright%20colors.%20They%20also%20offer%20excellent%20viewing%20angles%20so%20you%20can%20sit%20off%20to%20the%20side%20of%20the%20screen%20without%20noticing%20any%20drop%20in%20image%20quality.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20watching%20actual%20movies%20and%20TV%20shows%2C%20both%20displays%20provide%20impressive%20high-dynamic-range%20(%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fwhat-is-hdr-tv%5C%22%3EHDR%3C%2Fa%3E)%20performance.%20But%20while%20both%20TVs%20are%20neck%20and%20neck%20in%20most%20picture%20quality%20aspects%2C%20there%20is%20one%20area%20where%20the%20S95D%20has%20a%20more%20notable%20edge%20over%20the%20S95C%3A%20peak%20brightness.%20In%20fact%2C%20the%20S95D%20is%20the%20brightest%20OLED%20TV%20I've%20ever%20measured.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20a%2010%25%20HDR%20test%20pattern%20(a%20white%20box%20that%20takes%20up%2010%25%20of%20the%20screen)%2C%20I%20measured%20a%20peak%20of%20around%201%2C360%20nits%20on%20the%20S95C.%20On%20that%20same%20test%20pattern%2C%20I%20measured%20a%20peak%20of%20around%201%2C700%20nits%20on%20the%20S95D.%20That's%20an%20increase%20of%20340%20nits%20or%20about%2025%25%2C%20which%20is%20a%20solid%20jump.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20said%2C%20the%20S95D%20can%20only%20hit%201%2C700%20nits%20briefly%20before%20dimming%20significantly.%20But%20since%20most%20highlights%20that%20need%20to%20get%20that%20bright%20(like%20an%20explosion%20in%20a%20movie)%20only%20appear%20on%20screen%20for%20quick%20flashes%2C%20this%20limitation%20isn't%20that%20big%20of%20a%20deal.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUltimately%2C%20the%20S95D's%20increased%20brightness%20gives%20it%20a%20slight%20advantage%20over%20the%20S95C%20for%20two%20reasons.%20One%2C%20it%20gives%20you%20more%20headroom%20to%20adjust%20the%20S95D's%20settings%20and%20pump%20up%20the%20screen's%20brightness%20to%20help%20combat%20issues%20with%20glare%20in%20rooms%20that%20let%20in%20a%20lot%20of%20light.%20And%20two%2C%20it%20enables%20the%20S95D%20to%20more%20accurately%20cover%20the%20full%20range%20of%20brightness%20that%20filmmakers%20intend%20when%20mastering%20HDR%20content%20that%20exceeds%201%2C000%20nits.%20This%20means%20that%20extreme%20highlights%20can%20come%20through%20with%20a%20bit%20more%20detail%20and%20visual%20intensity%20on%20the%20S95D%20than%20they%20would%20on%20the%20S95C.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20while%20the%20S95D's%20brightness%20performance%20is%20the%20kind%20of%20thing%20that%20home%20theater%20nerds%20like%20me%20geek%20out%20over%2C%20it's%20important%20to%20note%20that%20the%20real-world%20benefits%20of%20this%20extra%20luminance%20can%20be%20subtle.%20If%20you%20watch%20both%20TVs%20next%20to%20each%20other%20while%20set%20in%20their%20brightest%20modes%20or%20playing%20HDR%20movies%20with%20especially%20bright%20highlights%20and%20colors%2C%20you'll%20certainly%20see%20a%20difference.%20But%20for%20average%20TV%20viewing%2C%20the%20S95C's%20brightness%20remains%20sufficient.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20while%20the%20S95D%20does%20technically%20deliver%20superior%20image%20quality%2C%20I%20don't%20think%20its%20performance%20benefits%20are%20big%20enough%20to%20justify%20its%20more%20expensive%20price%20tag.%20The%20S95D%20will%20eventually%20come%20down%20in%20price%2C%20and%20the%20S95C%20will%20sell%20out%2C%20so%20this%20will%20become%20a%20moot%20point.%20But%20for%20now%2C%20it's%20hard%20to%20justify%20spending%20so%20much%20when%20you%20can%20still%20snag%20the%20S95C%20for%20around%20%241%2C000%20less.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Glare%20and%20reflections%5C%22%3ESamsung%20S95D%20vs.%20S95C%3A%20Glare%20and%20reflections%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20scene%20from%20%26quot%3BThe%20Matrix%26quot%3B%20being%20displayed%20on%20a%20Samsung%20S95D%20TV.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F662c106410dfcda409641b7a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20S95D's%20matte%20screen%20(pictured%20above)%20is%20better%20at%20combating%20reflections%20than%20the%20S95C's%20glossy%20screen%2C%20but%20the%20anti-glare%20filter%20can%20elevate%20black%20levels.%20(Note%3A%20The%20camera%20sensor%20exaggerates%20this%20effect.)%3Cp%3ESteven%20Cohen%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20more%20so%20than%20their%20brightness%20capabilities%2C%20the%20biggest%20difference%20between%20the%20S95D%20and%20S95C%20is%20how%20each%20TV%20handles%20reflections.%20The%20S95C%20uses%20a%20glossy%20screen%2C%20while%20the%20S95D%20uses%20a%20matte%20screen.%20Both%20have%20their%20pros%20and%20cons%2C%20but%20the%20S95D's%20matte%20coating%20offers%20a%20big%20improvement%20in%20reducing%20glare%20and%20reflections.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGlossy%20screens%2C%20which%20are%20used%20in%20nearly%20every%20TV%20sold%2C%20can%20cause%20noticeable%20reflections%20in%20certain%20rooms.%20To%20combat%20this%2C%20manufacturers%20use%20different%20kinds%20of%20anti-reflective%20filters.%20The%20S95C's%20anti-reflective%20filter%20does%20a%20solid%20job%20for%20a%20screen%20of%20its%20type%2C%20but%20depending%20on%20where%20your%20windows%20and%20indoor%20lights%20are%20positioned%2C%20you%20could%20still%20run%20into%20issues%20with%20glare.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20the%20S95D's%20matte%20screen%20virtually%20eliminates%20reflections%20and%20glare%20entirely.%20If%20you%20struggle%20with%20reflections%20in%20your%20room%2C%20the%20S95D%20is%20a%20game%20changer.%20The%20only%20other%204K%20sets%20with%20similar%20matte-screen%20coatings%20are%20Samsung's%20own%20Frame%20TV%20and%20Hisense's%20upcoming%20Canvas%20TV%2C%20but%20those%20models%20can't%20match%20the%20pixel-level%20contrast%20that%20the%20S95D's%20OLED%20panel%20produces.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUnfortunately%2C%20the%20S95D's%20matte%20screen%20has%20one%20notable%20side%20effect%3A%20it%20hurts%20black-level%20performance%20in%20a%20bright%20room.%20Though%20reflections%20and%20glare%20are%20dramatically%20reduced%2C%20black%20levels%20lose%20a%20bit%20of%20that%20deep%2C%20inky%20quality%20that%20OLEDs%20are%20known%20for%20and%20instead%20look%20slightly%20gray%20and%20hazy.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20especially%20true%20when%20displaying%20darker%20scenes%2C%20like%20the%20opening%20action%20sequence%20of%20%26quot%3BThe%20Matrix.%26quot%3B%20This%20scene%20starts%20in%20a%20dimly%20lit%20room%20and%20then%20moves%20outside%20at%20night.%20The%20darkest%20elements%20of%20the%20scene%20are%20meant%20to%20be%20pure%20black%2C%20but%20because%20of%20the%20S95D's%20glare-free%20coating%2C%20they%20take%20on%20a%20more%20cloudy%20look%20that%20flattens%20the%20distinction%20between%20shades%20of%20black%20and%20gray.%20This%20makes%20it%20harder%20to%20discern%20details%20in%20shadows.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20S95C's%20anti-reflective%20filter%20isn't%20immune%20to%20this%20kind%20of%20side%20effect%20either%2C%20as%20it%20can%20cause%20a%20slight%20elevation%20of%20black%20levels%20and%20a%20faint%20pinkish%20hue%20in%20extremely%20bright%20rooms.%20But%20I%20never%20found%20those%20effects%20on%20the%20S95C%20noticeable%20during%20day-to-day%20viewing.%20In%20contrast%2C%20the%20elevated%20black%20levels%20caused%20by%20the%20S95D's%20matte%20screen%20are%20more%20pronounced%20and%20easier%20to%20notice.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20bright%20room%20viewing%2C%20there%20are%20clear%20tradeoffs%20with%20each%20TV.%20The%20S95D's%20matte%20screen%20can%20handle%20glare%20and%20reflections%20better%20than%20any%20other%20TV%20on%20the%20market%2C%20but%20the%20downside%20is%20that%20you%20get%20elevated%20black%20levels%20that%20can%20give%20some%20dark%20scenes%20a%20flat%20look.%20Conversely%2C%20while%20the%20S95C's%20glossy%20screen%20preserves%20deep%20black%20levels%20better%20in%20bright%20rooms%2C%20it's%20much%20more%20prone%20to%20showing%20reflections%20when%20hit%20with%20light%20from%20certain%20angles.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20big%20home%20theater%20enthusiast%2C%20I%20prefer%20the%20S95C's%20glossy%20screen%20since%20black-level%20performance%20is%20one%20of%20the%20most%20important%20aspects%20of%20preserving%20an%20accurate%20image.%20The%20matte%20screen%20is%20definitely%20helpful%20for%20certain%20use%20cases%20and%20could%20be%20ideal%20for%20specific%20setups%2C%20but%20I%20wish%20Samsung%20had%20implemented%20it%20on%20a%20step-down%20model%20rather%20than%20its%202024%20flagship.%20Or%20better%20yet%2C%20offered%20it%20as%20an%20optional%20alternative.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Design%20and%20interface%5C%22%3ESamsung%20S95D%20vs.%20S95C%3A%20Design%20and%20interface%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20side-by-side%20composite%20of%20a%20Samsung%20S95C%20next%20to%20an%20S95D%20TV%20with%20their%20interfaces%20displayed%20on%20each%20screen.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F663ce520b4abc992e8c74ae5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22771%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20S95C%20(left)%20compared%20to%20an%20S95D%2