0that%20have%20been%20followed%20for%20thousands%20of%20years.%20My%20village%20in%20Kinnaur%20is%20a%20gem%20of%20a%20mountain%20place.%20We%20have%20a%20very%20small%20population%20and%20the%20pollution%20level%20is%20almost%20zero%2C%E2%80%9D%20Ashish%2C%20who%20hails%20from%20Huri%20village%2C%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20his%20strong%20longing%2C%20he%20would%20be%20able%20to%20come%20back%20to%20his%20hometown%20only%20once%20a%20year.%20Eventually%2C%20in%202011%2C%20he%20quit%20his%20four-year-long%20career%20in%20mechanical%20engineering%20to%20move%20to%20his%20village%20permanently.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMore%20than%20the%20desire%20to%20reconnect%20with%20his%20roots%2C%20Ashish%20yearned%20to%20look%20after%20his%20ancestral%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F58210%2Ffruit-orchard-destinations-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eapple%20orchards%20%3C%2Fa%3Ethat%20were%20lying%20unattended.%20%E2%80%9CWhile%20Kinnaur%20is%20known%20worldwide%20for%20its%20apples%2C%20our%20orchards%20were%20abandoned%20as%20there%20were%20no%20young%20members%20in%20my%20family%20to%20look%20after%20them.%20The%20land%20was%20losing%20its%20richness%20and%20I%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20bear%20that.%20It%20was%20one%20of%20the%20prime%20reasons%20why%20I%20decided%20to%20come%20back%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FKinnaur-apples-2-1715174392.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Ashish%20adds%20that%20Kinnauri%20apples%20are%20one%20of%20the%20most%20expensive%20ones%20in%20the%20world%2C%20and%20yet%2C%20the%20apple%20growers%20never%20receive%20their%20fair%20share.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-