osis%20patients%2C%20Picture%20source%3A%20Facebook%3A%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fshisindia%2Fphotos%2Fpb.100064733584085.-2207520000%2F1647620488599433%2F%3Ftype%3D3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESHIS%20%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20since%201980%2C%20when%20Wohab%20and%20Pal%20started%20the%20SHIS%20Foundation%2C%20they%20have%20been%20trying%20to%20bring%20these%20services%20to%20the%20people%E2%80%99s%20doorsteps.%20Today%2C%20their%20resilience%20is%20reflected%20in%20the%20many%20programmes%20helmed%20by%20the%20foundation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20these%20is%20the%20tuberculosis%20control%20programme.%20The%20key%20objective%20of%20this%20project%20is%20to%20create%20demand%20and%20social%20support%20for%20TB%20diagnosis%20and%20improve%20access%20to%20diagnosis%20and%20treatment%20of%20TB%20through%20Directly%20Observed%20Treatment%20Short%20Course%20(DOTS)%20%E2%80%94%20the%20tuberculosis%20control%20strategy%20recommended%20by%20the%20World%20Health%20Organisation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThrough%20its%20clinics%20and%20volunteer%20base%2C%20SHIS%20is%20attempting%20to%20help%20hinder%20the%20progression%20of%20tuberculosis%20right%20at%20the%20onset.%20Wohab%20shares%20that%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F337918%2Fbengaluru-sanathya-foundation-provides-free-wheelchair-nebulizer-medical-equipment-on-rent%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20programme%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20one%20of%20their%20biggest%20chapters%20aside%20from%20the%20boat%20clinics.%20%E2%80%9CMore%20than%2040%2C000%20people%20have%20been%20able%20to%20manage%20their%20TB%20through%20the%20medicines%20that%20we%20provide%20them.%E2%80%9D%20He%20adds%20that%20they%20procure%20these%20medicines%20from%20the%20Government%20for%20free.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%2