s%20were%20fast%20disappearing%20due%20to%20modernisation%20and%20hunger%20for%20harvesting%20more%20produce%20in%20less%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CToday%2C%20we%20see%20only%20green-coloured%20ladyfingers%20in%20the%20market%20when%20there%20are%20several%20native%20variants%20including%20the%20red-coloured%20torpedo%20shaped%20variety%20and%20light%20green-coloured%20long%20elephant%20tusk%20variety%20that%20has%20more%20amount%20of%20amino%20acids%20and%20iron%20content.%20Similarly%2C%20we%20get%20only%20hybrid%20tomatoes%20even%20though%20we%20have%20more%20than%20200%20native%20tomato%20varieties%20with%20distinct%20tastes%20and%20nutritional%20content.%20Irrespective%20of%20their%20benefits%2C%20you%20won%E2%80%99t%20find%20those%20vegetables%20in%20markets%20at%20all%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20points%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20where%20have%20these%20vegetables%20disappeared%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CUnfortunately%2C%20we%20are%20forced%20to%20eat%20only%20genetically%20modified%20hybrid%20varieties.%20Genetically%20modified%20seeds%20only%20respond%20to%20chemical%20insecticides%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Naveen%2C%20%E2%80%9CHowever%2C%20we%20can%20reduce%20this%20dependency%20by%20growing%20our%20own%20vegetables.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnce%20every%20two%20years%2C%20he%20travels%20to%20Kolli%20hills%20%E2%80%94%20roughly%20400%20km%20from%20his%20home%20%E2%80%94%20to%20collect%20native%20varieties%20of%20seeds%20from%20tribal%20people%20in%20the%20region.%20%E2%80%9CAs%20the%20seeds%20I%20source%20are%20in%20limited%20numbers%2C%20I%20use%20them%20to%20grow%20produce%20at%20home.%20After%20harvesting%2C%20I%20scoop%20out%20the%20seeds%20in%20large%20quantities%20and%20then%20distribute%20them%20to%20the%20community.%20Using%20native%20seeds%2C%20farmers%20and%20gardeners%20do%20not%20need%20to%20buy%20seeds%20for%20the%20next%20season%2C%20and%20using%20a%20similar%20approach%2C%20they%20pass%20on%20seeds%20to%20others%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%2